      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know u aren't a doctor but i'm just trying to figure out if it's even an option. my doctor is out of the office until monday and the headache is making it hard to focus. like, is ibuprofen generally considered a \"no\" for CKD or can i just take a low dose like 200mg to get through the weekend?",
